            "title": "Distance to hedgerows drives local repulsion and attraction of wind turbines on bats: Implications for spatial siting",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Camille",
                    "lastName": "Leroux"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Christian",
